	Java package version to 1.3.0.
	* src/tclblend/tcl/lang/Interp.java: Moved
	name of tclblend shared lib into a variable.
	* src/tcljava/tcl/lang/BlendExtension.java:
	Updated Java package version to 1.3.0.
